    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i dont have a clinic appointment for like two weeks and my doctor is really busy. honestly it's not like i'm gasping for air, just a bit heavy in the chest when i move around. surely i can just take an extra puff of my salbutamol for a few days until i see him? it's probably fine if i just manage it at home for now.",
